aine"}, {"first_name": "Vincent", "last_name": "Descoeur", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Sylvie", "last_name": "Dezarnaud", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Fabien", "last_name": "Di Filippo", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Julien", "last_name": "Dive", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Virginie", "last_name": "Duby-Muller", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Forissier", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Philippe", "last_name": "Gosselin", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Justine", "last_name": "Gruet", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Michel", "last_name": "Herbillon", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Patrick", "last_name": "Hetzel", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Vincent", "last_name": "Jeanbrun", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Philippe", "last_name": "Juvin", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Corentin", "last_name": "Le Fur", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Guillaume", "last_name": "Lepers", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Thierry", "last_name": "Liger", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Eric", "last_name": "Li\u00e9geon", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Alexandra", "last_name": "Martin", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9rique", "last_name": "Meunier", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "J\u00e9r\u00f4me", "last_name": "Nury", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9ric", "last_name": "Pauget", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Christelle", "last_name": "Petex", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Alexandre", "last_name": "Portier", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Ray", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Vincent", "last_name": "Rolland", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Mich\u00e8le", "last_name": "Tabarot", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Pierre", "last_name": "Taite", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Louis", "last_name": "Thi\u00e9riot", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Antoine", "last_name": "Vermorel-Marques", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Pierre", "last_name": "Vigier", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}], "summary": "Le narcotrafic g\u00e9n\u00e8re d\u2019importants flux financiers illicites, favorisant le d\u00e9veloppement de pratiques de corruption qui menacent l\u2019int\u00e9grit\u00e9 des services publics. Des cas de compromission d\u2019agents ont d\u00e9j\u00e0 \u00e9t\u00e9 constat\u00e9s, facilitant l\u2019action des r\u00e9seaux criminels dans divers secteurs comme les forces de l\u2019ordre, les douanes, l\u2019administration p\u00e9nitentiaire ou les collectivit\u00e9s locales.\nCet amendement vise \u00e0 compl\u00e9ter l\u2019article\u00a022 de la proposition de loi en int\u00e9grant une obligation, pour l\u2019Agence fran\u00e7aise anticorruption, d\u2019\u00e9laborer une cartographie des risques de corruption li\u00e9s au narcotrafic. Cette cartographie permettra d\u2019identifier les vuln\u00e9rabilit\u00e9s et d\u2019orienter les politiques de pr\u00e9vention.\nLes administrations concern\u00e9es devront ensuite mettre en place des dispositifs adapt\u00e9s en fonction des risques identifi\u00e9s. Enfin, un rapport annuel transmis au Parlement garantira un suivi efficace et une am\u00e9lioration continue des mesures de lutte contre la corruption dans les services publics expos\u00e9s au narcotrafic.\nL\u2019ajout de cette disposition \u00e0 l\u2019article\u00a022 assure la coh\u00e9rence du texte en renfor\u00e7ant l\u2019arsenal de lutte contre l\u2019infiltration des r\u00e9seaux criminels dans les institutions publiques"}